# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:13
translate french jezq2_7e645245:

    # det "What are you going to do if we find your dad?"
    det "Qu'est-ce que tu vas faire si on retrouve ton père ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:14
translate french jezq2_b55c740c:

    # pc "I'm going to hug him. Tell him I'm sorry for the things that I said and did."
    pc "Je vais le serrer dans mes bras. Lui dire que je suis désolée pour les choses que j'ai dites et faites."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:15
translate french jezq2_ab3ff14b:

    # pc "Tell him I love him."
    pc "Lui dire que je l'aime."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:17
translate french jezq2_2e7485fd:

    # det "That's nice."
    det "C'est sympa."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:18
translate french jezq2_070ecc32:

    # pc "Then I guess I'll just keep on like I have been. Except I'll try to spend more time with him."
    pc "Et moi, je suppose que je vais continuer comme avant. Sauf que j'essaierai de passer plus de temps avec lui."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:19
translate french jezq2_84c06b07:

    # pc "I have a lot of questions for him."
    pc "J'ai plein de questions à lui poser."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:21
translate french jezq2_c85babbc:

    # det "And what if we find him, but he's... um..."
    det "Et si on le trouvait, mais qu’il était… euh…"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:22
translate french jezq2_64d707d2:

    # pc "Not alive?"
    pc "Mort ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:23
translate french jezq2_efaf6eb5:

    # det "Yeah."
    det "Oui."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:25
translate french jezq2_820bd703:

    # det "You don't have to answer that. I shouldn't have asked."
    det "Tu n’es pas obligé de répondre. Je n’aurais pas dû poser la question."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:26
translate french jezq2_2e4c59d4:

    # det "What a downer. I'm so bad at normal conversation."
    det "Quelle ambiance de morose. Je suis vraiment nulle en conversation normale."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:28
translate french jezq2_b219d344:

    # pc "It's okay."
    pc "Ce n’est pas grave."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:29
translate french jezq2_69298cee:

    # pc "If Dad's not alive, I would be sad, of course."
    pc "Si papa n’était plus en vie, je serais triste, bien sûr."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:30
translate french jezq2_ec2c3b68:

    # pc "I'd have a lot of regrets that I would have to live with."
    pc "J’aurais beaucoup de regrets avec lesquels je devrais vivre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:32
translate french jezq2_068843ff:

    # pc "I would just hope that somehow he'd know that I love him and I appreciate everything that he's done for me."
    pc "J'espérerais juste qu'il sache d'une manière ou d'une autre que je l'aime et que j'apprécie tout ce qu'il a fait pour moi."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:33
translate french jezq2_661a213e:

    # pc "And I'd try to live up to his expectations."
    pc "Et j'essaierais d'être à la hauteur de ses attentes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:35
translate french jezq2_29d642c1:

    # det "I'm sure that wherever he is, he knows how you feel."
    det "Je suis sûr que, où qu'il soit, il sait ce que tu ressens."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:36
translate french jezq2_31173ab5:

    # det "But I really hope that you get a chance to tell him."
    det "Mais j'espère vraiment que tu auras l'occasion de le lui dire."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:37
translate french jezq2_1f8cc682:

    # pc "Thanks, Jez. So do I."
    pc "Merci, Jez. Moi aussi."

